title: 'NEATH THE ARIZONA SKIES video quality upgrade

sources.title: 'NEATH THE ARIZONA SKIES video quality upgrade
sources.description: This print is sharper and cleaner than the existing IA copies. An entertaining John Wayne oater with fistfights, shootouts, lots of bad guys and a cute kid. Old reliables Gabby Hayes and Yakima Canutt are part of the B-western fun. Directed by Harry Fraser. US release 1934. UK release 1935. Complete print. a.k.a. "'Neath Arizona Skies". TRIVIA: Wayne and Canutt doubled for each other in some of the action sequences.
